summary:
Hi. 
Im Janka, 32 years old.
I came here from Slovakia.
I graduated from the business academy.
I got a certificate (administration and typescript)  from the University of Economics in Bratislava while studying at a high school.
I worked as a receptionist, administrative assistant, manager, invoicer for an online store, and others.
My personal skills are self-reliant but also team player (support-management), deadline oriented attitude, results oriented, fast learned, organized, methodical, relaxed and easy-going, hardworking, positive, thorough,...
